The information for this area was collected by Class 5H of Sandford St. Martin's First School. We would like to thank all those who helped us and answered our many questions.
The children who helped to collect this information were: Mark Burbidge, Colin Campbell, Gavin Dixon, Michael Dyer, Michael Grant, Paul Hawkins, Theo Holland, Stephen Ireson, Kevin Lench, Tyrone Maytum, Stephen Randall, Paul Scothern, Sorrel Butler, Helen Chisman, Joanne Cluskey, Donna Cole, Melanie Cross, Zoe Diment, Zoe Farris, Shelley Feltham, Emma Gauntlett, Shelley Hamblin, Elaine Lever, Sarah Miller, Helen Peters, Claire Pettyfer, Sarah Rhodes, Amber Smith, Anthea Williams, Lara Williams and Jennie Wills.
